{"tid":1999552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"瘋搶！菁雋131呎納米戶售240萬　9個月升值22%","createTime":"2020-05-03T09:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T11:18:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"63d5bf51ac788ee006c84ea0169b1a2ca65b773d","tid":1999552,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:04:13.000Z","msg":"納米樓辣招盤持貨僅約9個月即轉手。美聯謝志遠稱，屯門菁雋中層32室，實用面積131方呎，僅於去年7月以196.7萬元購入，其後以月租6,500元租出。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，單位約兩個月前開價250萬元放售，即以240萬元售出，呎價18,321元。料為該盤首宗二手買賣。原業主持貨不足一年，帳面賺43.3萬元，單位升值約22%。據了解，是次轉手須付15%額外印花稅由新買家支付。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200503/bkn-20200503110507056-0503_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200503%2Fbkn-20200503110507056-0503_00842_001.html&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=8bbaf993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200503/bkn-20200503110507056-0503_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ff29939a06036122be113df078c1cfef753b695d","tid":1999552,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ff9d19f74d4870f48117235e0c51ca207afd48","tid":1999552,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"★"},{"pid":"1cf2e8d14fd0a1aed8ae281a9d44d8d88ccd4de2","tid":1999552,"uid":3893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"是次轉手須付15%額外印花稅由新買家支付。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo